      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WINSLOW WISH (1) stalked the lead from a middle box and kept coming to win (23.67) at Horsham in Grade 5 over 410m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to be right there at the finish again. TICKET CONFETTI (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (25.87) in a Rank Limit - Grade 5 at Ballarat. Has a good record at this journey. Should be thereabouts. GLIMMER OF HOPE (8) drifted back from wide but charged home to hit the frame when 2.5 lengths from the winner (22.58) at Ballarat in Grade 5. Leading player again. WHIPSTICK SERENA (2) profiles nicely here at this trip.",
